  <brief_title>Anti-inflammatory Effect of Atorvastatin in Atherosclerotic Plaques Assessed by FDG-PET Imaging</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Atorvastatin on Inflammatory Atherosclerotic Plaques Assessed by FDG-PET Imaging</official_title>
