  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether HMG-CoA reductase inhibitor, atorvastatin
      attenuates inflammation in atherosclerotic plaques detected by 18F-fluorodeoxyglucose(FDG)
      PET.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
